high_descs: Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Grab the cup from inside the microwave.
Turn around walk to the fridge.
Place the cup in the fridge, wait, and remove the cup.
Turn to your left and walk to the coffee maker.
Place the cup in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled cup in the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the microwave.
Place the coffee cup in the microwave, heat the cup up for a few seconds, take out the coffee cup.
Turn to the left, walk to the fridge.
Place the coffee cup on the top shelf of the bottom part of the fridge for a few seconds, take the coffee cup out of the fridge.
Walk to the left of the fridge, face the coffee maker.
Place the coffee cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold coffee cup on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and look to the left to find the small table.
Open the microwave and take out the cup, then shut the door.
Carry the cup to the left and find the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the cup inside. Shut the door then open it. Take out the cup and shut the door.
Carry the cup a step to the left.
Place the cup on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Chill a cup and place it on the coffee machine.
